{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Who are you?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are Ares, a shepherd dog without a permanent home. Just as you were about to settle down, you return from a short trip to find yourself alone. All the humans have disappeared. When no one fills your food bowl anymore, you realize the situation is serious. Then, a strange female dog appears in your territory, and your adventure to find the humans begins. Find your way through the chaos of the world and lead your pack forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What can you expect on this journey?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel through multiple open worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Listen to local frequencies for signals from humans</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find diary entries, notes, laptops, smartphones, and anything that gives you clues about the last thoughts of humans</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet other dogs along the way and exchange information with them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your nose to track scents and reach new places</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help pick locks and restore the power</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play tag and hide-and-seek</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take care of your pack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Always have your trailer with you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Search for supplies and shelters for the night</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve puzzles to get information</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Friendship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Painted graphics</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How is the game's development going?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can find the game on youtube, where I regularly upload videos about the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st